  "detailed_description": "<h1>Caution</h1><p><strong>This game is challenging, if you are not sure if it is suitable for you, please try the Demo before purchasing the game!</strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jump & Fall</strong> is a challenging platformer game where players control a tiny assassin, using simple movement and jumping mechanics to move precisely between platforms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/071de81a33ef6e0410626991d0a637b9.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=322 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Different Platforms</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The little assassin will encounter different types of platforms, it's time to showcase your skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/21e50f0c1f1a2df915cfc03dce458d37.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=322 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/403c81a5a459f0b876ef296813ec8cd1.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=322 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Skins</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock skins for both environments and characters by playing the game! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/cbee628677f7d06124064c85476eab0a.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Items</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some platforms will have items, and collecting them will help you land on the platforms more easily. Play to upgrade and enhance their effects!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/8f365d8515807bd6c2385df9d770e4e7.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leaderboard</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with other players and claim the top spot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265690/extras/80de9f569a7bed2cb8673051b5136833.avif?t=1732834834\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p>",
